19. Conclusion

The blockchain module successfully implements an immutable document verification system for MedTwin AI. By storing only cryptographic hashes on the Polygon Amoy blockchain, the system ensures document authenticity while maintaining patient privacy. The module is designed to integrate seamlessly with the backend through a simple interface that accepts document hashes, making it suitable for secure healthcare record verification.

